  "comment": "Решение:\nТ.к. \\((x^2-9)^2 \\geq 0\\) и \\((x^2-2x-15)^2 \\geq 0, \\Rightarrow (x^2-9)^2+(x^2-2x-15)^2\\geq 0\\) только когда\n\\(\\begin{cases}x^2-9=0 (1) \\\\x^2-2x-15=0 (2)\\end{cases}\\)\n\\((1) x^2-9=0\\)\n\\((x-3)(x+3)=0\\)\n\\((2) x^2-2x-15=0\\)\n\\(D=4+60=64\\)\n\\(x_1=\\cfrac{2-8}{2}\\)\n\\(x_1=-3\\)\n\\(x_2=\\cfrac{2+8}{2}\\)\n\\(x_2=5\\)\n\\(\\begin{cases}(x-3)(x+3)=0 \\\\x=-3; x=5\\end{cases}\\)\n\\(\\begin{cases}x=3; x=-3 \\\\x=5; x=-3\\end{cases}\\)\n\\(\\Rightarrow x=-3\\\\\\)\nОтвет:\\(-3\\)",
